\f0\fs24 \cf0 World Venues revitalizes the concert-going experience for new media users by presenting live performances in a fun, interactive, sharable way. \ \ \ \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720
\i\fs36 \cf0 Venues are social hubs \i0\fs24 \ \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\slleading30\pardirnatural \cf0 Listening to music can be an intangible experience -- unless you experience it live. Chances are you\'92re listening to music inside a physical venue -- a place that\'92s been around for decades, if not centuries, that is chock full of music history, architectural characteristics and unique acoustic peculiarities.\ \ \'91World Venues\'92 celebrates those concert halls and opera houses of the world as center points of music appreciation. It re-frames what it is to listen to music by considering the auditory context as well as the performance itself. It\'92s an app about ambiance, architecture, history, as well as the physical experience of music.\ \ But more than just a stage, venues are hubs of social activity. It\'92s where music lovers convene, listen, love and share. Similarly, \'91World Venues\'92 draws from the opinions of the concertgoers and encourages users to participate. They can let friends know where they\'92ve been -- or where they want to go -- by bookmarking venues and sharing.\ \ \pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720
\i\fs36 \cf0 Donate\ \ \ Social\ \ \ Report Bugs}
